title: Magic Arrow

When you ''launch an arrow imbued with the power of a [[Magic]] move'', roll +Dex instead of [[+Magic]]. The effect instead originates from any creature or location you could shoot with an arrow. One creature targeted by the spell takes 1d4 [[Bonus Damage]].